    parentName: "ul"
  }, "Now, I hope you'll, I'm doing so much talking and you listen to me so intently, that I don't really give you the opportunity at this time to begin to develop grand strategy and try to integrate all the things that I am saying. But I have deliberately tried to present the things to you, coming from the whole to the particular in a way that we continually would have to realize that this is related to what I have heard before, and I am very eager that you feel the absolute interconnectedness of everything.", mdx("span", {
